~VS~
Concatinating&#58; &quot;5&quot;+&quot;4&quot; ===&gt; &quot;54&quot;
Concatinating&#58; &quot;5&quot;+&quot;5&quot;+&quot;5&quot;+&quot;5&quot; ===&gt; &quot;5555&quot;
Concatinating&#58; &quot;5&quot;+&quot;Mia&quot; ===&gt; &quot;5Mia&quot;
Concatinating&#58; &quot;Mama&quot;+&quot;Mia&quot; ===&gt; &quot;MamaMia&quot;
Concatinating&#58; &quot;Mama&quot;+&quot;&quot;+&quot;Mia&quot; ====&gt; &quot;Mama Mia&quot;[/code:31d6hclb]

